0: SELECT DISTINCT      d.ACTIVITY_TITLE,     s.SESSION_LOCATION,     t.TERM_START_DATE,     p.PERSON_NAME AS SUPERVISOR_NAME FROM      IAP_SUBJECT_DETAIL d JOIN      IAP_SUBJECT_SESSION s ON d.IAP_SUBJECT_SESSION_KEY = s.IAP_SUBJECT_SESSION_KEY JOIN      ACADEMIC_TERMS_ALL t ON d.TERM_CODE = t.TERM_CODE JOIN      IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON p ON d.IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON_KEY = p.IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON_KEY WHERE      p.PERSON_ROLE = 'Activity leader' ORDER BY      t.TERM_START_DATE ASC;	----- bird -----	dw
1: SELECT DISTINCT     FR.ROOM_FULL_NAME,     B.BUILDING_NAME,     B.BUILDING_STREET_ADDRESS,     FBA.CITY,     FBA.STATE,     FBA.POSTAL_CODE,     FB.BUILDING_HEIGHT FROM     FCLT_ROOMS FR JOIN     COURSE_CATALOG_SUBJECT_OFFERED CCO ON     CCO.MEET_PLACE = FR.FCLT_ROOM_KEY JOIN     FCLT_BUILDING_ADDRESS FBA ON     FBA.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY = FR.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY JOIN     FCLT_BUILDING FB ON     FB.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY = FR.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY JOIN     BUILDINGS B ON     B.BUILDING_KEY = FR.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY WHERE     CCO.DEPARTMENT_NAME = 'Computer Science' AND     FBA.ADDRESS_PURPOSE = 'STREET';	----- bird -----	dw
2: SELECT      fb.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY AS building_key,      fb.BUILDING_NAME AS building_name,      COUNT(DISTINCT cco.SUBJECT_ID) AS num_courses FROM      CIS_COURSE_CATALOG ccc JOIN      COURSE_CATALOG_SUBJECT_OFFERED cco ON ccc.SUBJECT_ID = cco.SUBJECT_ID JOIN      FCLT_ROOMS fr ON cco.MEET_PLACE = fr.FCLT_ROOM_KEY JOIN      FCLT_BUILDING fb ON fr.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY = fb.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY WHERE      fb.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY IS NOT NULL GROUP BY      fb.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY,      fb.BUILDING_NAME;	----- bird -----	dw
3: SELECT b.BUILDING_NAME, f.FLOOR FROM FAC_BUILDING b JOIN FAC_FLOOR f ON b.FAC_BUILDING_KEY = f.BUILDING_KEY WHERE f.FLOOR = (SELECT MAX(FLOOR) FROM FAC_FLOOR);	----- bird -----	dw
4: WITH ListMemberCount AS (     SELECT          ml.MOIRA_LIST_NAME,         COUNT(1) AS MemberCount     FROM          MOIRA_LIST ml     JOIN          MOIRA_LIST_DETAIL mld ON ml.MOIRA_LIST_KEY = mld.MOIRA_LIST_KEY     JOIN          SE_PERSON sp ON mld.MOIRA_LIST_MEMBER = sp.KRB_NAME     WHERE          ml.MOIRA_LIST_NAME LIKE 'B%'          AND ml.IS_MOIRA_MAILING_LIST = 'Y'         AND sp.ORGANIZATION = 'Electrical Engineering and Computer Science'     GROUP BY          ml.MOIRA_LIST_NAME ), MaxMemberList AS (     SELECT          MOIRA_LIST_NAME,          MemberCount     FROM          ListMemberCount     WHERE          MemberCount = (SELECT MAX(MemberCount) FROM ListMemberCount) ) SELECT      (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ListMemberCount) AS MailingListCount,      MaxMemberList.MOIRA_LIST_NAME AS ListWithMaxMembers,      MaxMemberList.MemberCount AS MaxMemberCount FROM      MaxMemberList;	----- bird -----	dw
5: SELECT      c.SUBJECT_TITLE,     COUNT(DISTINCT e.MIT_ID) AS number_of_instructors,     MAX(LENGTH(e.FULL_NAME)) AS longest_instructor_name_length FROM      COURSE_CATALOG_SUBJECT_OFFERED c JOIN      EMPLOYEE_DIRECTORY e ON c.RESPONSIBLE_FACULTY_MIT_ID = e.MIT_ID JOIN      ACADEMIC_TERMS_ALL a ON c.TERM_CODE = a.TERM_CODE WHERE      c.IS_OFFERED_SUMMER_TERM = 'Y' GROUP BY      c.SUBJECT_TITLE;	----- bird -----	dw
